item.title: Pwnscape base
item.dc:creator: @relmitos relmitos
item.description:
@relmitos wrote:

with the pwnscape base it shows the action button in your server shell when you click a icon.
the actionbutton is defined in clickingMost as case xxxx: where xxxx is the action button id.

just a suggestion, if you click on, for example the attack skill icon in your skills tab it also shows the action button.
you could make it teleport to a training area to train attack. or make it show a combat guide. etc…
